    <p>For even Rambert felt a nervous tremor at the thought that soon he would have to confront a love and a devotion that the plague months had slowly refined to a pale abstraction, with the <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="flesh-and-blood"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(有血有肉的/活生生的)</code></b> woman who had given rise to them.</p>
