    <p>For the sensation, confused perhaps, but none the less poignant for that, of all those days and weeks and months of life lost to their love made them vaguely feel they were <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="entitled to"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(有权享有/拥有...的资格)</code></b> some compensation;</p>
